{"tid":925600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲女留遺書　逸東邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-12-03T00:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T01:23:48.000Z","uid":160807,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef780e891a522b250a1181ffd282071ccc27a60","tid":925600,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/photo/bkn-20181202132317646-1202_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181202165658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181202132317646-1202_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181202165658&h=4d24a6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東涌有人高處墮下身亡。逸東邨悅逸樓，今午(2日)1時05分，有途人行經上址時，發現一名女子倒卧地上昏迷，懷疑她從高處墮下，慌忙報警求助。救護員趕赴現場，為女事主檢驗後證實明顯死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方以帳篷遮蓋遺體，經初步調查後，證實死者為一名姓楊(20歲)女子，相信楊從中層一個單位的洗手間一躍而下，警方在現場檢獲遺書，事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。據悉，楊近日因工作問題不開心，情緒低落，感到對不起家人。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=j2VufJ7sHyWA%2BEuaD8bPOUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a0dc15eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/bkn-20181202132317646-1202_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fbkn-20181202132317646-1202_00822_001.html&d=j2VufJ7sHyWA%2BEuaD8bPOUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3740b1c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/bkn-20181202132317646-1202_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"688cda6a4541e93a7ccd81f981657c30ce452fb1","tid":925600,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"窮人不要生"},{"pid":"72c62ae1572a47f06f68b8db572135d87f20a202","tid":925600,"uid":52943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:39:49.000Z","msg":"工作問題不開心<br />\n<br />\n為份工死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac29b16f50091d9afda212485cc193bbcd21d8ce","tid":925600,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"條橋帶黎唔少壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東涌本來都好舒服下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e350bf6eb204e943a2d286d8c7f976dbd162f01b","tid":925600,"uid":32455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72c62ae1572a47f06f68b8db572135d87f20a202","tid":925600,"uid":52943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:39:49.000Z","msg":"工作問題不開心<br />\n<br />\n為份工死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"觸發點嚟啫，應該本身情緒都唔多好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac998cf734166ef0d1ae9f5dd960dec35cd800e","tid":925600,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:08:26.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"3cb8b5240b2a890435110c4aadc7a41c6b1c456a","tid":925600,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:09:51.000Z","msg":"留遺書跳樓=高處墮下？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3939d21958350f473f059d312ea1819d3f62874","tid":925600,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:23:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}